{"id":117633,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/10/网友艾佛斯：我好乱啊/","date":"2010-10-28T17:29:11Z","modified":"2010-10-28T17:29:11Z","title":"网友艾佛斯：我好乱啊","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">网友</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a title=\"\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">艾佛斯</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：我好乱啊</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">今晨，程鹤麟发围脖说：“上周港媒纷纷报道，指携自用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">iPad</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">往内地要缴税。有人携</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">iPad</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">入境，以内存文件照片证明是自用，仍被征税千元。但东总</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">@</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">刘庆东 亲口告诉老程，他携</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">iPad</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">主动向海关申报，海关检查后说，旧的自用品不征税。于是他天天带进带出好不得意。有谁能告诉老程，先前那位是咋回事呢？”</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">同样是从香港携</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">iPad</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">进深圳，有人要缴税千元，刘庆东却不用缴税。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东总</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://t.sina.com.cn/n/%E5%88%98%E5%BA%86%E4%B8%9C\"><span>@</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">刘庆东</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">留言进一步证实其所言不虚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“我觉得是政策有调整。对我们这种在港深两地跑来跑去的人，不会对自用的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IPAD</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">征税。昨天晚上过深圳，福田口岸海关抽查，关员把我包内的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IPAD</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">拿起看了一眼，又放回去，问都没问。”</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">跟随的几则网友留 ……</p>\n<p>……</span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<p align=\"center\">\n<p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}